<div class="content-section">
    <div class="container gamecontainer">
        <div class="row">
            <div class="col-md-4">
                <h2>Hangman GUI</h2>
                <p>
                    A hangman game using Windows Forms in C#. The textbox allows for user input of one character at a time or the full word
                    as a valid guess. Either way can be used to solve the puzzle but an incorrect word or character guess is counted as a
                    wrong guess. Invalid input of special characters brings up a dialog box but is not counted against the user. The game includes
                    sound effects for wrong guesses and when the user wins or looses the game.
                </p>
            </div>
            <div class="col-md-8"><img src="http://zippy.gfycat.com/FlickeringNaughtyAquaticleech.gif" /></div>
        </div>
        <div class="row">
            <div class="col-md-2 gameEXElink"><a href="~/Content/Work/hangman.exe" class="btn btn-default btn-md"><i class="fa fa-download fa-fw"></i> <span class="network-name">Download</span></a></div>
            <div class="col-md-10 gameGithublink"><a href="https://github.com/ericfowler303/HangmanGUI" class="btn btn-default btn-md"><i class="fa fa-github fa-fw"></i> <span class="network-name">Source</span></a></div>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>
